:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1192336";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:4:"7664";s:6:"handle";s:4:"Anna";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1085";s:17:"recipient_user_id";s:3:"601";s:18:"recipient_username";s:5:"Shaze";s:4:"text";s:12:"In what way?";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420395531";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#fffb3b";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14203955331";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#f6ff88";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1192340;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1192340";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:4:"7664";s:6:"handle";s:4:"Anna";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1085";s:17:"recipient_user_id";s:3:"601";s:18:"recipient_username";s:5:"Shaze";s:4:"text";s:247:"I can kinda understand why Anna was pressing them, but that wasn&#039;t Anna herself, that was me. We did a whole roleplay where Zeus came by and was being a little jerk. I was hoping that someone was going to tell the whole story of what happened";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420395760";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#fffb3b";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14203957621";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#f6ff88";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1192341;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1192341";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:4:"7664";s:6:"handle";s:4:"Anna";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1085";s:17:"recipient_user_id";s:3:"601";s:18:"recipient_username";s:5:"Shaze";s:4:"text";s:98:"You guys were kind of just like &quot;Yeah, he was being rude. Whatever, don&#039;t know him&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420395803";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#fffb3b";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14203958048";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#f6ff88";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1192345;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1192345";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:3:"601";s:6:"handle";s:5:"Shaze";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"227";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:4:"Anna";s:4:"text";s:629:"You were really forcing yourself on us I feel, like... you kept asking questions we had no way of answering, and then answering them yourself anyways. I think instead of having Anna just happen to come find the Ponies Zeus had talked to in order to explain everything. Zeus himself could have taken what Felicity said to heart and used it as an experience to grow. And what did you really expect from us? Our characters did not know him, Felicity had met him once before, Tetsu had met shim for the first time that day. For all they knew that WAS how he usually was. You were basically asking us things we had no way to answer :(";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420395937";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#6e00ff";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14203959382";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#6e00ff";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1192350;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1192350";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:4:"7664";s:6:"handle";s:4:"Anna";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1085";s:17:"recipient_user_id";s:3:"601";s:18:"recipient_username";s:5:"Shaze";s:4:"text";s:381:"No, I just wanted them to explain what happened in the roleplay that was atleast a hour long. Sure they didn&#039;t know them, but they were talking to him for a good 20 minutes. That&#039;s why I was having her say &#039;Why wasn&#039;t he home when I got there?&#039; one of them could of said &#039;Oh because he was talking to us for about 20 minutes about.... [roleplay]&quot;";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420396085";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#fffb3b";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14203960871";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#f6ff88";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1192353;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1192353";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:4:"7664";s:6:"handle";s:4:"Anna";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1085";s:17:"recipient_user_id";s:3:"601";s:18:"recipient_username";s:5:"Shaze";s:4:"text";s:286:"Anna had no idea what happened. Zeus doesn&#039;t know Fel either, so why would he take it to heart? I was hoping Anna could figure out what happened, then discuss it with him because he would actually listen to her so he could grow! Zeus is far from perfect, and I do want him to learn";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420396153";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#fffb3b";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14203961555";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#f6ff88";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1192356;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1192356";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:3:"601";s:6:"handle";s:5:"Shaze";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"227";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:4:"Anna";s:4:"text";s:171:"But thats not what our characters would have done, We did exactly what our characters would have done. She asked, we did our best to answer and point her in his direction.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420396213";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#6e00ff";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14203962154";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#6e00ff";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1192358;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1192358";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:4:"7664";s:6:"handle";s:4:"Anna";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1085";s:17:"recipient_user_id";s:3:"601";s:18:"recipient_username";s:5:"Shaze";s:4:"text";s:141:"When did they explain what happened at the basketball court? All they told her was that he was being rude, and that he went back to the house";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420396257";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#fffb3b";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14203962595";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#f6ff88";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1192361;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1192361";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:4:"7664";s:6:"handle";s:4:"Anna";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1085";s:17:"recipient_user_id";s:3:"601";s:18:"recipient_username";s:5:"Shaze";s:4:"text";s:192:"Honestly it kind of made that whole RP at the court pointless, other than getting a few ponies to hate Anna and Zeus. I was planning on fixing that, justifying what Zeus did and make him learn";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420396317";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#fffb3b";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14203963190";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#f6ff88";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1192362;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1192362";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:3:"601";s:6:"handle";s:5:"Shaze";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"227";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:4:"Anna";s:4:"text";s:225:"All they said was that they assumed he was going to the lake with his boat... That was all. I don&#039;t recall either of themn saying he went back to the house. And I am sorry the RP did not go the way you had scripted it...";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420396407";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#6e00ff";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14203964094";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#6e00ff";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1192366;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1192366";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:4:"7664";s:6:"handle";s:4:"Anna";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1085";s:17:"recipient_user_id";s:3:"601";s:18:"recipient_username";s:5:"Shaze";s:4:"text";s:329:"It&#039;s not like what I wanted to happen was illogical, I wanted Zeus to learn from his mistake. But nothing happened because Felecity is a stranger to him and he wouldn&#039;t believe what she said, and Anna (His mother) had no idea what happened, so she can&#039;t correct him either. Now it&#039;s just going to happen again";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420396501";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#fffb3b";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14203965031";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#f6ff88";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1192370;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1192370";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:3:"601";s:6:"handle";s:5:"Shaze";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"227";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:4:"Anna";s:4:"text";s:118:"Alright... I really don&#039;t know what you want from me V_V. Our characters did EXACTLY what they would have done...";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420396593";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#6e00ff";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14203965950";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#6e00ff";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1192372;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1192372";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:4:"7664";s:6:"handle";s:4:"Anna";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1085";s:17:"recipient_user_id";s:3:"601";s:18:"recipient_username";s:5:"Shaze";s:4:"text";s:107:"That roleplay just made me feel like I had no idea what I was doing, and quite frankly, made me feel stupid";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420396682";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#fffb3b";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14203966836";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#f6ff88";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1192374;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1192374";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:3:"601";s:6:"handle";s:5:"Shaze";s:12:"character_id";s:3:"227";s:17:"recipient_user_id";N;s:18:"recipient_username";s:4:"Anna";s:4:"text";s:11:"I am sorry.";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420396701";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#6e00ff";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14203967036";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#6e00ff";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1192381;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1192381";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:4:"7664";s:6:"handle";s:4:"Anna";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1085";s:17:"recipient_user_id";s:3:"601";s:18:"recipient_username";s:5:"Shaze";s:4:"text";s:241:"It&#039;s fine, really. Truly I&#039;m not mad, I&#039;m just saying how I feel. I was more upset about it yesterday. Sometimes your character will act a certain way, yes, but for the sake of the rroleplay you can turn that just a little bit";s:9:"timestamp";s:10:"1420396890";s:15:"chat_name_color";s:7:"#fffb3b";s:9:"chat_rand";s:11:"14203968920";s:15:"chat_text_color";s:7:"#f6ff88";s:16:"chat_log_type_id";s:1:"2";s:6:"viewed";N;}i:1192384;a:14:{s:11:"chat_log_id";s:7:"1192384";s:12:"chat_room_id";s:1:"1";s:7:"user_id";s:4:"7664";s:6:"handle";s:4:"Anna";s:12:"character_id";s:4:"1085";s:17:"recipient_user_id";s:3:"601";s:18:"recipient_username";s:5:"Shaze";s:4:"text";s:190:"All I was asking wa